<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>아이디 찾기</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,typography"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: "#8B5CF6", // Violet-500
            "background-light": "#F9FAFB", // Gray-50
            "background-dark": "#1F2937", // Gray-800
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ["Noto Sans KR", "sans-serif"],
          },
          borderRadius: {
            DEFAULT: "0.5rem", // 8px
          },
        },
      },
    };
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
<header class="flex justify-between items-center py-6">
<button class="flex items-center text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-icons mr-2">home</span>
<span class="font-medium">홈 버튼</span>
</button>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
<button class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors font-medium">로그인</button>
<button class="bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-violet-600 transition-colors font-medium">회원가입</button>
</div>
</header>
<main class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
<div class="text-center mb-8">
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">아이디 찾기</h1>
<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">가입 시 등록한 정보로 아이디를 찾아보세요.</p>
</div>
<form class="space-y-6">
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" for="name">이름</label>
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-background-light dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-colors" id="name" placeholder="이름 입력" type="text"/>
</div>
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" for="birthdate">생년월일</label>
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-background-light dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-colors" id="birthdate" placeholder="생년월일 입력 (예: 19900101)" type="text"/>
</div>
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1" for="email">Email</label>
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-background-light dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-colors" id="email" placeholder="email 입력" type="email"/>
</div>
<button class="w-full bg-primary text-white py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-violet-600 transition-colors font-bold flex items-center justify-center space-x-2" type="submit">
<span>인증메일 발송</span>
<span class="material-icons">send</span>
</button>
</form>
</main>
</div>

</body></html>